OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Thousands of people in England with a  
OL,6, genetic condition that raises their    
OL,7, risk of bowel cancer by up to 80% will 
OL,8, be given regular cancer checks.        
OL,10,FThe move will save lives by detecting  
OL,11,Fcancers early in people with Lynch     
OL,12,Fsyndrome, the NHS says.                
OL,14,FThe condition is thought to affect     
OL,15,F175,000 people in England, but few are 
OL,16,Faware they have it.                    
OL,18,FA simple blood test can identify it -  
OL,19,Fthose affected can have a colonoscopy  
OL,20,Fevery two years from a young age.      
